name: Cyborg
biography: Half man, half machine - all hero! After a near fatal incident, Victor Stone was cybernetically enhanced by his father. He now possesses the ability to communicate, manipulate, and interface with nearly all forms of technology. As he is constantly upgrading, he promises to defend the future from any threat. He is also a founding member of the Teen Titans and in some continuities, the Justice League.

first_appearance.name: Between Friend and Foe; Where Nightmares Begin; Whatever Happened to Sargon the Sorcerer

creator: George Pérez
